DEAD OR ALIVE 5 Last Round Settings Fix-BAT


DEAD OR ALIVE 5 Last Round *Settings Fix* (c) Team NINJA

Release Date: 30/03/2015 Protection: Steam
Cracked By: BAT-TEAM # of Files: one

Note:

This small fix will allow you to set graphics settings
and use them in the game!

Experience the intuitive fighting system, gorgeous
characters and blockbuster stages of Dead or Alive 5 in
this definitive series finale!

Two new playable characters join to make 34 fighters - the
largest roster in series history!

Master the signature DOA fighting system through the rich
story and tutorial modes, unlock more costumes than ever
before in each of the offline training modes, and compete
with the best fighters in the world in the full-featured
online training modes. Fight as ninjas, assassins
roughnecks & wrestlers as you knock your opponents off an
exotic waterfall, into an exploding oil rig and more!

The final word in fighting entertainment - Dead or Alive 5
Last Round!

1. Unpack release
2. Copy the files to your game installation directory
3. Use startup_setting.bat to set the settings and game.bat
to launch the game using those settings
4. Enjoy! :wink
